1
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:28,200
♪Confessing to the moon
in the rustling wind back then♪

2
00:00:28,200 --> 00:00:34,440
♪Like a boat being swallowed up
among the cities♪

3
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:41,440
♪Watching the flowers fall in unease,
worries and troubles fill my mind♪

4
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:48,240
♪Am I going to where I want♪

5
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,960
♪To stay or to leave, you decide♪

6
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:54,960
♪Nations are different♪

7
00:00:55,280 --> 00:01:01,520
♪One without desire
is one that is not alive♪

8
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:04,560
♪Looking at the sky side by side♪

9
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:08,320
♪We've gotten closer with time♪

10
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:15,120
♪One glance,
the city of Chang'an is bare♪

11
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:22,360
♪Among the ridiculous people
and things is me♪

12
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:30,360
=Dream of Chang'An=

13
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:33,080
=Episode 37=

14
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,240
(This place is?)

15
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,520
(That is me.)

16
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,560
(So, His Majesty has hidden
the fake body)

17
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,160
(over here.)

18
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:09,800
Come out.

19
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,280
You followed me all the way here.

20
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,120
Were you not planning to see me?

21
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:30,840
Your Majesty.

22
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,520
Your Majesty,

23
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,880
you did recognise me.

24
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,480
Your Majesty, I have not failed my duty.

25
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,640
I have returned alive.

26
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:58,920
Yu'er.

27
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,160
By the way, Your Majesty,

28
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,720
how is your injury?

29
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:31,760
Your Majesty,

30
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,560
what's wrong?

31
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,120
Return to your master and tell him

32
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,160
that if he wants my offspring,

33
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,040
he can just drug me.

34
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,520
There's no need to go through
all of this trouble

35
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,520
and find a fake Yu'er to dupe me.

36
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:53,920
Your Majesty,

37
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,840
I'm the real Cheng Ruoyu.

38
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,720
Your Majesty, I'm the real Yu'er.

39
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,000
Please put down your sword.

40
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,480
You are seriously injured.

41
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,840
You mustn't lose your temper.

42
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,040
Don't you recognise

43
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,040
my voice?

44
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,200
Look.

45
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,520
I am the real Cheng Ruoyu.

46
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,600
And, you knew what happened

47
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,600
within the Chess of Generals Camp.

48
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,440
The story that you have made up
is indistinguishable from the truth.

49
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:58,000
(We have found a girl)

50
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,440
(with looks identical to Cheng Ruoyu.)

51
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,600
(She is good at sophistry.)

52
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,040
(We have ordered her)

53
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,080
(to learn the martial arts
of Violet Bureau.)

54
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,400
(Her name will be Ling Ling.)

55
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,600
(She will follow us on our expedition.)

56
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,800
(She will return to the Capital under
the pretence of capturing the emperor.)

57
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,080
(We will make our plans
accordingly after that.)

58
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,280
What are these?

59
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,600
These are the secret letters

60
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,080
that I have intercepted from
the Chess of Generals Camp.

61
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,880
You fooled the emperor to cross the sea,

62
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,200
and you came back to life. Great job.

63
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,560
Your Majesty, that isn't the case.

64
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,640
You must trust me.

65
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,480
You want me to trust you?

66
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,600
Seeing you as you rise from the dead,

67
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:37,000
it makes me sympathise more with myself.

68
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,000
You will give birth to my offspring

69
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,600
so that Qiu Ziliang will be able

70
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,920
to control the next emperor,

71
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,560
am I right?

72
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,200
Your Majesty,

73
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,400
are you doing this
out of bitter reasons?

74
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,840
Who do you think you are?

75
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,400
How dare you pretend to be my Yu'er?

76
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,000
Scram.

77
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,640
Your Majesty.

78
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,760
Scram!

79
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:46,200
(Yu'er,)

80
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:48,840
(I'm sorry.)

81
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,480
(Please don't blame me for this.)

82
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:20,920
You're back.

83
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,640
Have you met Qi Yan?

84
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:25,000
It's no wonder you're letting me
meet His Majesty.

85
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,920
Why are you angry with me?

86
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,840
Qi Yan was the one who didn't want to
acknowledge your existence.

87
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,640
You should be angry with him.

88
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,120
It's all because

89
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,120
you spread false information
with the secret letters.

90
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,640
If not, he wouldn't fall for it.

91
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:37,640
Do you think I wouldn't fall for
the tricks of others?

92
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,640
No matter what people say about you,

93
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,440
you're the only one whom I trust.

94
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,080
I'm sure she hates you to the core.

95
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:57,720
She hates me?

96
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,400
It's better than her struggling

97
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,720
to sever her ties from Qi Yan.

98
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:02,840
Do you not plan

99
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,800
to tell her the truth?

100
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:12,840
I don't know what to do either.

101
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,400
Your Majesty.

102
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:38,280
Your Majesty,

103
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,360
it's time for you to take your medicine.

104
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,280
(Seeing you as you rise from the dead,)

105
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,600
(it makes me sympathise more
with myself.)

106
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:45,720
(You will give birth to my offspring)

107
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:47,400
(so that Qiu Ziliang will be able)

108
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:49,080
(to control the next emperor,)

109
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,320
(am I right?)

110
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,720
(Return to your master and tell him)

111
00:10:53,920 --> 00:10:54,840
(that if he wants my offspring,)

112
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:56,760
(he can just drug me.)

113
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,360
(There's no need to go through
all of this trouble)

114
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,000
(and find a fake Yu'er to dupe me.)

115
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,400
(Now that I think about it,)

116
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,520
(it's normal for His Majesty)

117
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,480
(not to acknowledge my existence.)

118
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:08,360
(With the secret letters)

119
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,280
(and the fake body,)

120
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,480
(he wouldn't trust my words
that easily.)

121
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,400
(Who do you think you are?)

122
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,720
(How dare you pretend to be my Yu'er?)

123
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,280
(Scram!)

124
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:20,600
My Yu'er?

125
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,320
I'm sure

126
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:30,240
it's because His Majesty
cares too much about Yu'er.

127
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:32,120
That's why he's not acknowledging
Ling Ling's existence.

128
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:34,200
(Yes.)

129
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:35,560
(I'm sure that's the case.)

130
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,200
(I mustn't be frustrated
because of this.)

131
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:38,920
(I mustn't fall for
Qiu Ziliang's tricks.)

132
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,120
(Cheng Ruoyu,)

133
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,640
(let's give this another try.)

134
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:45,200
(I'm sure His Majesty will
recognise me sooner or later.)

135
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:01,840
Have you straightened out your thinking?

136
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,320
What do you mean?

137
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,160
It's getting late.

138
00:12:06,640 --> 00:12:08,800
You should sleep in my room.

139
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,160
Chess Overseer,

140
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,320
the room is ready.

141
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:18,920
Both of you may leave.

142
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:19,600
Understood.

143
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:32,720
What are you trying to do?

144
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:34,000
Are you going to place me
under house arrest?

145
00:12:35,680 --> 00:12:36,600
You are overthinking it.

146
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:37,360
If so,

147
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,520
why aren't I getting my own room?

148
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,080
I don't want to sleep
in the same room as you.

149
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,000
Staying in my room is more convenient.

150
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,480
No one will spy on you in here.

151
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:48,800
I have plenty of things
I want to teach you.

152
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:50,640
You're planning to teach me?

153
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:52,400
Music, chess, calligraphy, painting,

154
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:54,040
Astronomy and Geography,

155
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,760
the Five Elements and Eight Trigrams,

156
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,120
mystic skills,

157
00:12:57,800 --> 00:13:00,720
I will teach you everything.

158
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,320
Have you solved it?

159
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,440
What kind of nonsense is this?

160
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,880
This is too difficult for me!

161
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,120
If so, how did you manage to understand

162
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,040
the Ninth Heaven Mystic Maiden Formation
in one go back then?

163
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,880
You actually knew about that?

164
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:41,400
I know everything

165
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,960
that has happened in your life.

166
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:48,360
Qiu Yanzhi,

167
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,120
seems like you had spent

168
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:52,520
a huge amount of effort
to take me under your wing.

169
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,720
It's good that you know that.

170
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:58,400
The palace's celebration banquet

171
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,200
will be starting soon.

172
00:14:00,880 --> 00:14:01,560
Wait.

173
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,440
I thought you promised me

174
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,120
that I can put an end

175
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,120
to my relationship with His Majesty?

176
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:08,080
You had met His Majesty yesterday.

177
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:12,240
You should give me another chance.

178
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:14,040
Yesterday's meeting was too hasty.

179
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,280
That doesn't count.

180
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:17,000
I haven't given up on him yet.

181
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,360
You do say everything
that is on your mind

182
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,280
without thinking it through.

183
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:22,680
Fine.

184
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,920
I'm not a heartless person.

185
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:27,080
If you can solve this formation,

186
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:28,920
I will allow you to go.

187
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,840
Your Majesty,

188
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:52,560
the banquet is ready.

189
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,440
We await your presence.

190
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,240
Did Ling Ling attend the banquet?

191
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:01,400
I don't think so.

192
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:04,400
All right.

193
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:35,760
I want to go out

194
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:36,480
and take a breather.

195
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,000
I swear

196
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,080
that I won't escape.

197
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:44,760
I'm serious.

198
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,640
I'm here to see Prince Guang

199
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:07,920
under Chess Overseer's order.

200
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:09,359
I have important matters
to discuss with him.

201
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:19,440
Prince Guang.

202
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:20,200
Yu'er?

203
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:21,960
Please save me.

204
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,960
Official Zhang, please.

205
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,560
I'm done.

206
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:13,600
Did you fall asleep?

207
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,280
Did you solve the formation?

208
00:19:27,560 --> 00:19:30,720
So, this is how you solve the formation.

209
00:19:33,040 --> 00:19:34,240
Your Highness, you're amazing indeed.

210
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,720
You're very knowledgeable

211
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:36,680
when it comes to traps and formations.

212
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,320
This formation is exceptional.

213
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:43,640
Where did you get this from?

214
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:46,080
Yanzhi showed me this formation
in order to test me.

215
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,520
She's teaching you this

216
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:49,840
for your own good.

217
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,560
I think she just wants to
make things difficult for me.

218
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,160
She's doing it deliberately so that
I won't be able

219
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:53,960
to enter the palace and see His Majesty.

220
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:55,360
Enter the palace?

221
00:19:57,800 --> 00:19:58,600
I don't know

222
00:19:58,600 --> 00:19:59,240
if I can make it in time.

223
00:19:59,360 --> 00:20:00,040
Farewell.

224
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:01,160
Thank you, Prince Guang.

225
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,360
Yu'er.

226
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:15,000
I've committed a bad deed

227
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,520
even though I was well-intentioned.

228
00:20:25,840 --> 00:20:26,560
I solved the formation.

229
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,640
You better keep your words.

230
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:28,320
Farewell.

231
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:56,400
Prince Guang.

232
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:34,120
Did I ruin your plan?

233
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:40,040
Were you referring to the formation?

234
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:44,800
I didn't know that she was going to
see His Majesty

235
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,760
after solving the formation.

236
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,200
It's fine.

237
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,800
No one was able to stop her anyway.

238
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,160
Ever since

239
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:56,400
you taught her the
Ninth Heaven Mystic Maiden Steps,

240
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:57,880
ordinary soldiers

241
00:21:58,360 --> 00:21:59,480
have no way to catch up with her.

242
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,080
Yu'er does have innate talent

243
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:06,800
for learning martial arts.

244
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:10,240
How does she fare
compared with Qiu Ziliang?

245
00:22:13,680 --> 00:22:14,920
Yu'er is broad-minded.

246
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:16,840
If she can focus on
improving her martial arts

247
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:18,080
and be well-acquainted
with the ways of the world,

248
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:20,120
she will be able

249
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:22,360
to surpass Qiu Ziliang.

250
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:25,280
Are you sure?

251
00:22:26,520 --> 00:22:27,160
I am.

252
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:30,400
Since ancient times,
good always triumphs over evil.

253
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,200
Your Highness,

254
00:22:56,080 --> 00:22:56,800
thank you.

255
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:05,120
You will never be able to imagine

256
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:08,200
how important it is for me

257
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:10,920
to learn

258
00:23:11,280 --> 00:23:12,360
that Ruoling is still alive.

259
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:18,880
And you, who told me about this fact,

260
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,560
are very important to me as well.

261
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,200
How do you plan

262
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,360
to make them cut their ties?

263
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:52,640
As long as His Majesty
doesn't acknowledge her existence,

264
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:55,360
their ties will be cut eventually.

265
00:24:03,640 --> 00:24:04,520
But, will His Majesty

266
00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:07,720
be able to do so?

267
00:24:25,080 --> 00:24:25,880
Eunuch Cheng.

268
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:29,800
Sorry for being late.

269
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:47,520
Who are you?

270
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:49,800
Are you Yu'er?

271
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:52,600
I thought you were dead?

272
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:54,000
Eunuch Cheng,

273
00:24:54,320 --> 00:24:55,120
I am Ling Ling.

274
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:56,200
I was late because
I had something to attend to.

275
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,680
Can you bring me in?

276
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,560
You resemble her too much.

277
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:03,600
The resemblance is uncanny.

278
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,080
