Yu'er!

307
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:15,400
Uncle.

308
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:16,240
Cheng Huaizhi.

309
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:18,480
Your Majesty.

310
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:19,520
Your Majesty.

311
00:26:28,040 --> 00:26:28,600
Uncle,

312
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:30,160
