313
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:31,440
Your Majesty,

314
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:32,680
this is Yu'er.

315
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,600
Your Majesty, she's still alive.

316
00:26:37,520 --> 00:26:38,160
Your Majesty.

317
00:26:40,120 --> 00:26:41,000
She isn't Yu'er.

318
00:26:43,560 --> 00:26:44,760
Yu'er is dead.

319
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,520
Your Majesty.

320
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,080
I am right in front of you.

321
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:52,920
My body,

322
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:53,720
my voice,

323
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:54,760
my hands, my feet,

324
00:26:54,760 --> 00:26:55,800
my entire being, and my heart,
