325
00:26:55,960 --> 00:26:56,760
Why are you

326
00:26:56,760 --> 00:26:57,640
ignoring me?

327
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,280
Even if you are similar

328
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:09,600
to Yu'er in every way,

329
00:27:10,520 --> 00:27:11,680
you are not Yu'er.

330
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:13,360
I

331
00:27:14,760 --> 00:27:16,080
