332
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:20,400
Your Majesty.

333
00:27:20,880 --> 00:27:21,480
Your Majesty!

334
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:23,000
Are you not acknowledging my existence

335
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:24,400
