my existence.

351
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:26,640
You're indeed a warrior of sacrifice

352
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,960
of the Chess of Generals Camp.

353
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,520
Not only do you bear an uncanny
resemblance to her,

354
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,920
