386
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,360
But, I am jealous.

387
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,760
Although you're going to marry Qi Yan,

388
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:31,880
I know you did so

389
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,160
out of revenge.

390
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,800
But, when I see Prince Guang,

391
00:30:39,080 --> 00:30:40,000
