00:30:58,120 --> 00:30:59,280
Ru Feng!

396
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,480
Ru Feng!

397
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:03,680
Ru Feng!

398
00:31:06,360 --> 00:31:07,320
Did you see that?

399
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:11,400
