410
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:56,400
Why aren't you acknowledging
my existence?

411
00:32:45,320 --> 00:32:46,120
Your Majesty.

412
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,520
Ru Feng, good boy.

413
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:57,160
You do listen to me indeed.

414
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,040
Bring it to the stables.

415
00:33:07,560 --> 00:33:08,400
Your Majesty,

416
00:33:09,320 --> 00:33:12,040
I think she is Yu'er.

417
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,160
Huaizhi,

418
00:33:15,840 --> 00:33:16,600
your niece,

419
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,120
Cheng Ruoyu, is dead.

