422
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:25,880
Yes, Your Majesty.

423
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,760
(Ru Feng couldn't recognise me.)

424
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,320
(Uncle couldn't recognise me.)

425
00:33:55,520 --> 00:33:57,000
(His Majesty couldn't
recognise me as well.)

426
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,120
(So,)

427
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,640
