432
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,040
(All right.)

433
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,520
(I will live every day to the fullest
for the next five years.)

434
00:35:10,640 --> 00:35:11,360
(But,)

435
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,440
(Your Majesty, you need to be prepared.)

436
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:16,560
(Your Majesty, you might die within five
months if the condition becomes worse.)

437
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:18,440
You are still young.

438
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:22,240
And I,

439
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:26,440
won't be able to live for long.

440
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,480
Instead of

441
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,640
letting you take the risk

442
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,880
and return to my side,

443
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,840
I would rather

444
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:44,720
let you stay with Yanzhi.

445
00:35:46,800 --> 00:35:48,560
