446
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,680
(After tonight's departure,)

447
00:36:09,520 --> 00:36:10,720
(I'm afraid there would be no way)

448
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:11,440
(for me to return
to this place anymore.)

449
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:13,600
(Farewell,)

450
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:15,200
(Changming Palace.)

451
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,080
(Farewell,)

452
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,080
(Your Majesty.)

453
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,440
Yu'er,

454
00:36:44,080 --> 00:36:45,560
