469
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,200
I can only follow you back.

470
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,280
Congratulations.

471
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,720
You have finally embraced reality.

472
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:42,520
