to learn.

474
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:47,920
You have no time to throw a fit.

475
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:50,760
And,

476
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,440
you do have a home.

477
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:58,240
From now on,

478
00:38:59,360 --> 00:39:00,480
the places I go

479
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:03,280
