498
00:42:48,600 --> 00:42:49,520
I thought

499
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,840
you would continue to see Qi Yan.

500
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,680
until he acknowledges your existence.

501
00:42:53,120 --> 00:42:54,560
Actually,

502
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:58,040
