I was still alive.

512
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:17,600
So,

513
00:43:18,120 --> 00:43:19,360
no matter how terrible

514
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:20,080
your advice may sound before,

515
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:21,840
